  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bus Gemunu postponed till tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Private policy makers will be given until tomorrow (27) to decide on how to increase bus fares in line with the increased fuel prices. President of the Car Owners' Association Gemunu Wijeratne says.",
        "He stated at a media briefing held in Colombo today that if the bus fares were to be revised on July 01, their buses would have to be refueled at the old prices.",
        "He said that through the increase in fuel prices alone, the cost of buses has increased by about 6 percent and other factors should be taken into consideration while increasing bus fares.",
        "Mr. Wijeratne said that he was opposed to the action taken to increase fuel prices on the people in order to activate loss making institutions and condemned it."
      ],
